Brooklyn’s new home for independently made arcade games

 
 

1186 Broadway Brooklyn NY 11221. Sun-Thurs 5pm-2am, Fri-Sat 5pm-4am
Take the J train to Kosciuszko Street to arrive at our door step, or walk 10 minutes from the Myrtle Ave M.

Bring Your Vaccine Cards!

There are new rules from the CDC and the state of New York concerning vaccinated individuals. If you are visiting Wonderville and have proof of vaccination (either your card, a photo of your card, or the Excelsior Pass) please bring it along! We now require proof of vaccination to enter.

 
 
 
 

Become a Member!

Become a member on WithFriends to get discounts on merch and arcade admission! Memberships are split 50/50 between Wonderville and our in-house nonprofit Death By Audio Arcade!
